76561198062970876,Recommended,235620,15287354,"Posted: 9 April, 2015",all,VaultHunterArgus,"I bought this after playing the physical version with my brother and seeing it on TableTop on Geek & Sundry. It is a fun tactical board game with the main objective being to have the most gold at the end of a set number of turns (depending on how many players there are). In addition to Single Player against AI, there is both Online and Local Multiplayer (Local has the option of playing one on one or against each other and the AI, not sure if Online has the same option, as I haven't tried it yet as of writing this). There's plenty of races and abilities to try out, which are randomized each game and there are 3 expansions available as DLC, adding more races and abilities to what is already in the base game. Definitely recommend this, especially if you get it on sale like I did."
